sequenceDiagram
  actor Analyst
  participant Web as Next.js Console
  participant API as NestJS API
  participant Engine as Fraud Engine
  participant AI as Risk Analysis Service
  participant DB as Operational Store
  participant WS as WebSocket Gateway

  Web->>API: Submit transaction/login/device event
  API->>Engine: Evaluate rules, behaviour, graph and AML signals
  Engine->>AI: Request hybrid risk score and explanation
  AI-->>Engine: Score, reasons and recommended action
  Engine->>DB: Store decision and evidence
  alt High-risk event
    Engine->>DB: Create alert / investigation case
    API->>WS: Publish fraud.alert and operating.picture
    WS-->>Web: Push live update
    Analyst->>Web: Review alert, payment, graph and case
    Web->>API: Submit disposition / feedback
    API->>DB: Record outcome and audit event
  else Low-risk event
    API-->>Web: Return approved decision
  end
